org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Predictability.RTComponentModel

Interface CHRtSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CHRtSpecificationImpl

    public interface CHRtSpecification
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'CH Rt Specification'. The following attributes are deprecated: -respT -blockT operationReqForSporadicOcc: the list of operations that need to be invoked to allow the sporadic occurrence of the "context" operation. Constraints: Only for sporadic occurrence kind. The operations in the list must be owned by the Component which owns the 'context' operation. If the list is not empty the "context" operation must have private visibility and it cannot be invoked directly by other operations. If the list is empty the "context" operation must be invoked directly by other operations. CHRtSpecification extends MARTE RtSpecification

    The following features are supported:

    • Part With Port
    • WCET
    • Local WCET
    • Relative Priority
    • Ceiling
    • Memory Size Footprint
    • Stack Size
    • Heap Size
    • Slot
    • Base Comment
    • Occ Kind
    • Protection
    • Rl Dl
    • Context
    • Resp T
    • Block T
    • Operation Req For Sporadic Occ
    See Also:
    RTComponentModelPackage.getCHRtSpecification()
